		<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Advanced RISC Machines, Ltd.
		Семейство <A HREF="http://www.arm.uk.linux.org/">ARM</A> (StrongARM
		SA-1110, XScale, ARM6, ARM7, ARM2, ARM250, ARM3i, ARM610, ARM710,
		ARM720T, ARM920T) 
		</P>
		<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in">Axis Communications <A HREF="http://developer.axis.com/software/">ETRAX</A>
		(&quot;CRIS&quot; RISC-архитектура) 
