	Linux Users and Enthusiasts</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.dlug.de/">Dьsseldorfer
	Linux Users Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.epos.demon.co.uk/">Essex
	Linux User Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.linux.org.il/">Israeli
	Group of Linux Users</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.lug.or.kr/">Korean
	Linux Users Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.linux.org.mx/">Linux
	Mйxico</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.luga.or.at/">Linux
	User Group Austria</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.lugor.org/">Linux
	User Group of Rochester</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.lugs.org.sg/">Linux
	User Group of Singapore</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.nllgg.nl/">Nederlandse
	Linux Gebruikers Groep (Netherlands Linux Users Group or NLLGG)</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.ntlug.org/">North
	Texas Linux Users Group</A> 
	</P>
