	Carleton Linux Users Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.plugfr.org/">Provence
	Linux Users Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://linux.spb.org/">St.
	Petersburg Linux User Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.tlug.jp/">Tokyo
	Linux Users Group</A> 
	</P>
	<LI><P STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><A HREF="http://www.linux.org.tr/">Turkish
